pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Collagen Protein Bar Chocolate 45g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

15g Protein
0.1g Sugars
With Collagen peptides
No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives

Our Pro-active Nutrition products help your body shine from the inside out. Since 1991

Product Claims: 15g Protein, 0.1g Sugars, With Collagen peptides, No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives

Size: 45g

Flavour: Chocolate

Serving Size: 45g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence

Warnings

Contains: Milk and Soy.
May Contain: Gluten Containing Cereals (Wheat, Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

CAUTION

Excess consumption may have a laxative effect.

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Aussie Bodies® Protein Blend (34%) [Milk Protein, Collagen Peptides Powder (10%), Calcium Caseinate (Milk), Whey Protein Isolate (Milk), Emulsifier (Mono- and Di-glycerides of Fatty Acids)], No Added Sugar Dark Chocolate (23%) (Cocoa Mass, Cocoa Butter, Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Steviol Glycosides), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Flavour), Sweetener (Sorbitol), Humectant (Glycerol), Sweetener (Polydextrose), Cocoa Powder, Caramel Flavoured Crisps (2%) (Sweetener (Isomalt), Natural Flavour), Vegetable Oil, Natural Flavour, Salt, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin).

Contains: Contains: Milk and Soy.
May Contain: Gluten Containing Cereals (Wheat, Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Soy

Allergen May Be Present: Almonds| Hazelnuts| Oats| Peanuts| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Wheat| Cereals Containing Gluten

Directions

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C. Keep out of direct sunlight.
